<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Marketing">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#E60000">
    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.webmanifest">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="/icon-192.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <title>Surtitodo Marketing Panel</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #E60000;
            --secondary: #111111;
            --accent: #FFC300;
            --bg-color: #f4f6f8;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #333333;
            --border-radius: 12px;
        }

        body { 
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; 
            background: var(--bg-color); 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 20px 20px 200px 20px; 
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        /* Cabecera */
        .header { 
            background: var(--secondary); 
            color: var(--accent); 
            padding: 25px 20px; 
            border-radius: var(--border-radius); 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
        .header p { margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #dddddd; font-weight: 500; }

        /* Tarjetas de Configuración */
        .config-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .config-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .config-card h2 {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: var(--secondary);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .form-group:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #555;
        }

        select, input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            background: #fdfdfd;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }

        select:focus, input[type="text"]:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(230,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* Pestañas y Buscador */
        .inventory-header {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .tabs { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
        
        .tabs button { 
            background: #f0f0f0; 
            border: none; 
            padding: 10px 20px; 
            font-size: 15px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; 
            font-weight: 600; 
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .tabs button.active { 
            background: var(--primary); 
            color: white; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(230,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .search-box { 
            flex: 1; 
            min-width: 250px; 
            max-width: 400px;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        /* Grilla de Productos */
        .grid { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); 
            gap: 20px; 
        }

        .card { 
            background: white; 
            padding: 15px; 
            border-radius: var(--border-radius); 
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); 
            text-align: center; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            border: 3px solid transparent; 
            transition: all 0.2s ease; 
            position: relative;
        }

        .card:hover { 
            transform: translateY(-5px); 
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); 
        }

        .card.selected { 
            border-color: var(--primary); 
            background: #fffafa; 
        }

        .card img { 
            width: 120px; 
            height: 120px; 
            object-fit: contain; 
            margin-bottom: 12px; 
        }

        .card h3 { 
            font-size: 14px; 
            margin: 0 0 8px 0; 
            color: #333; 
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .badge-promo { 
            position: absolute; 
            top: -10px; 
            right: -10px; 
            background: var(--accent); 
            color: var(--secondary); 
            padding: 6px 12px; 
            border-radius: 20px; 
            font-size: 13px; 
            font-weight: 800; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); 
        }

        .btn-cargar-mas { 
            display: none; 
            margin: 40px auto; 
            background: var(--secondary); 
            color: white; 
            border: none; 
            padding: 12px 30px; 
            border-radius: 50px; 
            font-size: 16px; 
            font-weight: 600; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; 
            transition: 0.2s; 
        }

        .btn-cargar-mas:hover { 
            background: #333; 
            transform: scale(1.02); 
        }

        /* Barra de Acción Inferior — Dock */
        .bottom-action-bar {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.97);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            box-shadow: 0 -4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 10px 14px calc(10px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px));
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 100;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            transform: translateY(100%);
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .bottom-action-bar.visible {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .dock-inner {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 640px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .dock-contador {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2px 0;
        }

        .dock-contador strong {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .dock-btn-campana {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 13px 16px !important;
            font-size: 14px !important;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E60000, #ff4444) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(230,0,0,0.25);
        }

        .dock-seccion-reel {
            background: #f4f6f8;
            border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .dock-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.6px;
            color: #888;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .dock-select-reel {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            background: white;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .dock-acciones-principales {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .dock-btn-reel {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 10px !important;
            font-size: 14px !important;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
        }

        .dock-btn-volante {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 10px !important;
            font-size: 14px !important;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
        }

        .dock-btn-ab {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px !important;
            font-size: 13px !important;
            border-radius: 10px !important;
            background: #f0f0f0 !important;
            color: #333 !important;
            box-shadow: none !important;
        }

        .action-group {
            display: none;
        }

        .btn-action {
            border: none; 
            padding: 12px 25px; 
            border-radius: 50px; 
            font-size: 16px; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; 
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: white; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(230,0,0,0.3); }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: #cc0000; transform: translateY(-2px); }
        
        .btn-dark { background: var(--secondary); color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
        .btn-dark:hover { background: #000; transform: translateY(-2px); }

        #cargando-video {
            font-weight: 600; 
            color: var(--primary); 
            font-size: 14px; 
            background: #fff0f0;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: none;
        }

        /* Modal */
        .modal { 
            display: none; 
            position: fixed; 
            top: 0; left: 0; 
            width: 100%; height: 100%; 
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); 
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center; 
            z-index: 1000; 
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            padding: 10px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .modal-content { 
            background: white; 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: var(--border-radius); 
            text-align: center; 
            max-height: 90vh; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .modal-content img { 
            max-height: 50vh; 
            object-fit: contain; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            border: 1px solid #eee; 
        }

        /* --- MODO OSCURO --- */

        body.dark-theme div[id="contenedor-cliente-oferta"] {
            background: #2a2010 !important;
            border-color: #554422 !important;
        }
        body.dark-theme div[id="contenedor-tutorial"] {
            background: #2a2a2a !important;
            border-color: #444 !important;
        }

        body.dark-theme {
            --bg-color: #121212;
            --card-bg: #1e1e1e;
            --text-main: #e0e0e0;
            --secondary: #000000;
        }

        body.dark-theme .config-card,
        body.dark-theme .inventory-header,
        body.dark-theme .modal-content {
            border-color: #333;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        body.dark-theme .bottom-action-bar {
            background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.95);
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
        }

        body.dark-theme input[type="text"], 
        body.dark-theme select, 
        body.dark-theme textarea {
            background: #2a2a2a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            border-color: #444;
        }

        body.dark-theme .tabs button { background: #333; color: #aaa; }
        body.dark-theme .tabs button.active { background: var(--primary); color: white; }
        
        body.dark-theme .card { border-color: #333; background: #1e1e1e; }
        body.dark-theme .card h3 { color: #e0e0e0; }
        body.dark-theme .card.selected { background: #2a1111; border-color: var(--primary); }
        
        body.dark-theme .action-group { background: #2a2a2a; border-color: #444; }
        
        body.dark-theme .modal-content div[style*="background: #f8f9fa"] {
            background: #2a2a2a !important;
            border-color: #444 !important;
        }

        body.dark-theme .config-card h2 {
            color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom-color: #444; 
        }

        body.dark-theme .form-group label {
            color: #e0e0e0; 
        }

        /* --- iPad / móvil --- */
        .network-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            color: #a8dadc;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            border: 1px solid #2a3a5c;
        }

        .network-banner strong { color: #f1faee; }
        .network-banner code {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .sugerencias-bar {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 16px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .sugerencias-bar span {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            margin-right: 4px;
        }

        .btn-sugerencia {
            background: #fff5f5;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-sugerencia:hover { background: var(--primary); color: white; }

        .validacion-panel {
            display: none;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .validacion-panel.visible { display: block; }
        .validacion-panel.error { background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; color: #991b1b; }
        .validacion-panel.warning { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fde68a; color: #92400e; }
        .validacion-panel.ok { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; color: #166534; }

        .validacion-panel ul { margin: 6px 0 0 18px; padding: 0; }

        .presets-lista {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
            max-height: 160px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .preset-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 10px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .preset-item button {
            border: none;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .preset-item .btn-borrar {
            background: #e0e0e0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .historial-panel {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .historial-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 13px;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .historial-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        .historial-item .meta { color: #888; font-size: 12px; }

        .historial-item .acciones { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

        .historial-item button {
            border: none;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .historial-item button.btn-repetir { background: var(--primary); color: white; }

        .btn-campana {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E60000, #ff4444) !important;
        }

        /* Tier 2 */
        .modo-remate-banner {
            display: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff1f2, #ffe4e6);
            border: 2px solid #fda4af;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .modo-remate-banner.visible { display: block; }

        .modo-remate-banner h3 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: #e11d48;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .modo-remate-banner p {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .calendario-panel {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .calendario-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 13px;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .calendario-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        .calendario-item .fecha-badge {
            background: #fff5f5;
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .biblioteca-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(80px, 1fr));
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .biblioteca-item {
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            background: #f8f8f8;
        }

        .biblioteca-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        body.dark-theme .dock-seccion-reel {
            background: #252525;
            border-color: #444;
        }

        body.dark-theme .dock-select-reel {
            background: #2a2a2a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            border-color: #555;
        }

        body.dark-theme .bottom-action-bar {
            background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.97);
            border-color: #444;
        }

        .lote-panel {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }

        .lote-preview {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .lote-resultados-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .lote-resultado-item {
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #fafafa;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .lote-resultado-item img,
        .lote-resultado-item video {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            object-fit: cover;
            background: #000;
        }

        .lote-resultado-item p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 8px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #444;
        }

        .lote-resultado-item button {
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px;
            font-size: 11px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .campana-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        }

        .campana-grid img {
            width: 100%;
            max-height: 22vh;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            background: #f8f8f8;
        }

        .modal-campana-content {
            max-width: 700px;
            width: 95%;
            max-height: 92vh;
            padding: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .modal-campana-header {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            padding: 16px 20px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .modal-campana-header h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        .modal-campana-body {
            flex: 1;
            min-height: 0;
            overflow-y: auto;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            padding: 14px 16px;
        }

        .modal-campana-footer {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            padding: 12px 16px calc(12px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px));
            border-top: 2px solid #eee;
            background: #fafafa;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .modal-campana-footer .footer-label {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #888;
        }

        .modal-campana-footer .footer-label:not(:first-child) {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .modal-campana-acciones {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .modal-campana-acciones .btn-action,
        .modal-campana-acciones a.btn-action {
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        #campana-reel-video {
            max-height: 28vh;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            background: #000;
        }

        #campana-copy {
            width: 100%;
            height: 90px;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            resize: none;
            font-size: 12px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body.dark-theme .modal-campana-footer {
            background: #252525;
            border-color: #444;
        }

        body.dark-theme .modal-campana-header {
            border-color: #444;
        }

        .btn-whatsapp {
            background: #25D366 !important;
            color: white !important;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .campana-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .ios-hint {
            display: none;
            background: #fff8e6;
            border: 1px solid #ffd666;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #664d03;
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .ios-hint.visible { display: block; }

        .loading-overlay {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.75);
            z-index: 2000;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        }

        .loading-overlay.visible { display: flex; }

        .loading-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 320px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        .loading-spinner {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border: 4px solid #f0f0f0;
            border-top-color: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite;
            margin: 0 auto 16px;
        }

        @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

        .progress-bar-wrap {
            width: 100%;
            height: 8px;
            background: #eee;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 16px 0 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-bar-fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: 0%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), #ff4444);
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: width 0.4s ease;
        }

        #loading-porcentaje {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .modal-content video {
            width: 100%;
            max-height: 50vh;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            background: #000;
        }

        .modal-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            body { padding: 12px 12px 220px 12px; }

            .header { padding: 20px 16px; }
            .header h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; }

            .config-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

            .inventory-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
            }

            .tabs { flex-wrap: wrap; }

            .tabs button {
                flex: 1;
                min-width: calc(50% - 5px);
                padding: 12px 10px;
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            .search-box {
                min-width: 100% !important;
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .card { padding: 10px; }
            .card img { width: 90px; height: 90px; }

            .bottom-action-bar {
                padding: 8px 10px calc(8px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0px));
            }

            .dock-acciones-principales {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .modal-content {
                padding: 20px;
                max-height: 95vh;
                overflow-y: auto;
            }
        }

        @media (hover: none) {
            .card:hover { transform: none; }
            .btn-primary:hover, .btn-dark:hover { transform: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header" style="position: relative;">
        <button id="theme-toggle" onclick="toggleTheme()" style="position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border: none; font-size: 20px; cursor: pointer; padding: 10px; border-radius: 50%; transition: 0.3s;" title="Cambiar tema">
            🌙
        </button>
        
        <h1>⚙️ Panel de Marketing Surtitodo</h1>
        <p>Generador Automático de Contenido Digital</p>
    </div>

    <div id="network-banner" class="network-banner" style="display: none;">
        <strong>📱 Acceso desde iPad:</strong> Conecta tu iPad a la misma WiFi y abre Safari en<br>
        <code id="ipad-url">cargando...</code>
    </div>

    <div class="sugerencias-bar">
        <span>⚡ Sugerencias:</span>
        <button class="btn-sugerencia" onclick="aplicarSugerencia('topOfertas')">🔥 Top ofertas del día</button>
        <button class="btn-sugerencia" onclick="aplicarSugerencia('mejorDescuento')">💰 Mejor descuento %</button>
        <button class="btn-sugerencia" onclick="aplicarSugerencia('estancados')">⚠️ Estancados urgentes</button>
    </div>

    <div id="validacion-panel" class="validacion-panel"></div>

    <div class="historial-panel">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            <h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: var(--secondary);">📂 Historial de campañas</h2>
            <button onclick="cargarHistorial()" style="border: none; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px;">🔄 Actualizar</button>
        </div>
        <div id="historial-lista"><p style="color: #888; font-size: 13px; margin: 0;">Sin campañas guardadas aún.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="config-layout">
        
        <div class="config-card">
            <h2>🎨 1. Estilo y Formato</h2>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Formato (Cantidad de Productos):</label>
                <select id="selector-plantilla" onchange="cambiarLimitePlantilla()">
                    <option value="4">Grid 4 Productos</option>
                    <option value="2">Grid 2 Productos</option>
                    <option value="1">1 Producto Destacado</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Línea Gráfica (Estilo):</label>
                <select id="selector-tema">
                    <option value="clasico">🔴 Clásico Surtitodo</option>
                    <option value="carnaval">🥳 ¡Gran Carnaval!</option>
                    <option value="vip">⚫ VIP Premium</option>
                    <option value="fruver">🟢 Frescura Natural</option>
                    <option value="mercado">🍅 Estilo Mercado</option>
                    <option value="ecommerce">🛒 Exclusivo Web</option>
                    <option value="sorpresa">😱 Precios de Locura</option>
                    <option value="lanzamiento">✨ Nuevo Ingreso (Estreno)</option>
                    <option value="comunicado">📢 Comunicado (Cierre 3 de Abril)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Tamaño del Lienzo:</label>
                <select id="selector-orientacion">
                    <option value="feed">Post Cuadrado (1080x1350)</option>
                    <option value="historia">Historia / Estado (1080x1920)</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="config-card">
            <h2>📝 2. Textos Publicitarios</h2>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Título Principal:</label>
                <select id="selector-titulo" onchange="verificarTituloManual()">
                    <option value="Dias De Ahorro">Dias De Ahorro</option>
                    <option value="Gran Madrugón">Gran Madrugón</option>
                    <option value="Quincena de Ofertas">Quincena de Ofertas</option>
                    <option value="Especial de Carnes">Especial de Carnes</option>
                    <option value="Cyber Surtitodo">Cyber Surtitodo</option>
                    <option value="PERSONALIZADO">✏️ Escribir mi propio título...</option>
                </select>
                <input type="text" id="input-titulo-manual" placeholder="Ej: Feliz Día Mamá" style="display: none; margin-top: 10px;">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Etiqueta Promocional (Tagline):</label>
                    <select id="selector-tagline">
                        <option value="Solo por tiempo limitado">Solo por tiempo limitado</option>
                        <option value="¡Aprovecha hoy mismo!">¡Aprovecha hoy mismo!</option>
                        <option value="Precios imbatibles">Precios imbatibles</option>
                        <option value="Exclusivo Web">Exclusivo Web</option>
                        <option value="AVISO IMPORTANTE">AVISO IMPORTANTE</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="config-card">
            <h2>⭐ Presets / Favoritos</h2>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Guardar configuración actual:</label>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
                    <input type="text" id="input-preset-nombre" placeholder="Ej: Viernes carnes" style="flex: 1;">
                    <button onclick="guardarPreset()" class="btn-action btn-dark" style="padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 13px; white-space: nowrap;">💾 Guardar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="presets-lista" class="presets-lista">
                <p style="color: #888; font-size: 13px; margin: 0;">No hay presets guardados.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="config-card">
            <h2>📁 Biblioteca de assets</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin: 0 0 10px; line-height: 1.4;">Logos, banners y fotos reutilizables para campañas.</p>
            <input type="file" id="input-biblioteca" accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/jpg,image/webp" multiple
                   style="width: 100%; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px;" onchange="subirABiblioteca(this)">
            <div id="biblioteca-grid" class="biblioteca-grid"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="config-card">
            <h2>📦 Generación en lote</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin: 0 0 10px; line-height: 1.4;">
                Cola automática: genera varios volantes o reels uno tras otro sin intervención manual.
            </p>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Tipo de lote:</label>
                <select id="selector-tipo-lote" class="dock-select-reel" style="width:100%;" onchange="previewLote()">
                    <option value="volantes_por_linea">🛒 Volante por cada línea (top ofertas)</option>
                    <option value="remate_por_linea">⚠️ Remate: volante por línea (estancados)</option>
                    <option value="formatos_volante">🖼️ Feed + Historia (selección actual)</option>
                    <option value="reels_multi">🎬 4 reels distintos (misma selección)</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div id="lote-preview" class="lote-preview">Selecciona un tipo y pulsa Vista previa.</div>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <button type="button" onclick="previewLote()" class="btn-action btn-dark" style="flex:1; padding:10px; font-size:13px;">👁️ Vista previa</button>
                <button type="button" id="btn-iniciar-lote" onclick="iniciarLote()" class="btn-action btn-primary" style="flex:2; padding:10px; font-size:13px;">▶️ Iniciar cola</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="config-card">
            <h2>🎬 3. Videos Especiales</h2>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Selecciona el tipo de video a generar:</label>
                <select id="selector-video-especial" onchange="cambiarVideoEspecial()">
                    <option value="tutorial">📱 Video Tutorial Automático</option>
                    <option value="cliente_oferta">🎉 Reel: Oferta Ganada (Cliente)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div id="contenedor-tutorial" style="display: block; margin-top: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #fdfdfd; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #eaeaea;">
                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666; margin-top: 0; line-height: 1.4;">
                    Genera un Reel automático enseñando a los clientes cómo usar Surtitodo Ideal, usando la grabación base que ya está en el sistema.
                </p>
                <button id="btn-tutorial" class="btn-action btn-dark" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 10px; padding: 12px; font-size: 14px;" onclick="generarTutorial()">
                    ✨ Generar Reel Tutorial
                </button>
            </div>

            <div id="contenedor-cliente-oferta" style="display: none; margin-top: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #fffcf0; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #ffeeba; border-left: 4px solid #FFC300;">
                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666; margin-top: 0; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    Sube la foto de tu cliente y sus datos para crear un Reel de celebración "Nivel Pro".
                </p>
                
                <form id="form-reel-cliente" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;">
                    <div>
                        <input type="text" id="clientName" name="clientName" placeholder="👤 Nombre (Ej. Juan Pérez)" required 
                               style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #ccc; font-size: 13px;">
                    </div>
            
                    <div>
                        <input type="text" id="propertyAddress" name="propertyAddress" placeholder="📍 Mensaje o Dirección" required 
                               style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #ccc; font-size: 13px;">
                    </div>
            
                    <div>
                        <label style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #555; margin-bottom: 5px; display: block;">📸 Foto del Cliente:</label>
                        <input type="file" id="clientFoto" name="clientFoto" accept="image/png, image/jpeg, image/jpg" required
                               style="width: 100%; padding: 8px; background: #fff; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #ccc; font-size: 12px;">
                    </div>
            
                    <button type="button" id="btn-reel-cliente" onclick="generarReelCliente()" class="btn-action btn-primary"
                            style="width: 100%; margin-top: 5px; padding: 12px; font-size: 14px;">
                        🎬 Generar Reel Pro
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    
    <div id="modo-remate-banner" class="modo-remate-banner">
        <h3>⚠️ Modo Remate / Liquidación</h3>
        <p>Productos estancados seleccionados. Aplica el preset agresivo con plantilla de impacto, copy de urgencia y reel brutalista.</p>
        <button onclick="aplicarPresetRemate()" class="btn-action btn-primary" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 13px;">🔥 Activar preset remate</button>
    </div>

    <div id="calendario-panel" class="calendario-panel">
        <h2 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; color: var(--secondary);">📅 Calendario de campañas</h2>
        <div id="calendario-lista"><p style="color: #888; font-size: 13px; margin: 0;">Cargando...</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="inventory-header">
        <div class="tabs">
            <button id="tab-ofertas" class="active" onclick="cambiarPestana('ofertas')">🔥 Ofertas Activas</button>
            <button id="tab-todos" onclick="cambiarPestana('todos')">🛒 Todo el Catálogo</button>
            <button id="tab-estancados" onclick="cambiarPestana('estancados')" style="color: #e11d48; background: #ffe4e6; border: 1px solid #fda4af;">⚠️ Zona de Remate</button>
        </div>
        
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; flex: 1; min-width: 250px; justify-content: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <select id="filtro-linea" class="search-box" style="flex: 1; min-width: 150px; cursor: pointer; padding: 12px; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;" onchange="reiniciarYRenderizar()">
                <option value="">🛒 Todas las Líneas</option>
            </select>
            <input type="text" id="buscador" class="search-box" style="flex: 2; min-width: 200px;" placeholder="🔍 Buscar producto por nombre..." oninput="reiniciarYRenderizar()">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="grid-productos" class="grid">
        <p style="grid-column: 1/-1; text-align: center; color: #666; padding: 40px;">Cargando inventario desde el servidor Surtitodo...</p>
    </div>

    <button id="btn-cargar-mas" class="btn-cargar-mas" onclick="cargarMas()">⬇️ Cargar 50 productos más</button>

    <div id="action-container" class="bottom-action-bar">
        <div class="dock-inner">
            <div id="dock-contador" class="dock-contador"><strong>0</strong> productos seleccionados</div>

            <button id="btn-campana-completa" class="btn-action dock-btn-campana" onclick="generarCampanaCompleta()">
                🚀 Campaña completa
            </button>

            <div class="dock-seccion-reel">
                <p class="dock-label">Plantilla de reel</p>
                <select id="selector-plantilla-video" class="dock-select-reel">
                    <option value="PromoReel">💥 Explosivo</option>
                    <option value="ReelElegante">✨ Elegante</option>
                    <option value="ReelBrutalismo">🚧 Brutalista (Impacto)</option>
                    <option value="ReelLanzamiento">🚀 Nuevo Lanzamiento</option>
                    <option value="ReelAraStyle">🛒 Impacto (1 producto)</option>
                    <option value="ReelTemporada">🌟 Especial Temporada</option>
                    <option value="ReelCinematico">🎥 Cinemático 3D</option>
                    <option value="ReelCarnaval">🍉 Carnaval Frutas</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="dock-acciones-principales">
                <button id="btn-generar-video" class="btn-action btn-dark dock-btn-reel" onclick="generarVideoRemotion()">
                    🎬 Crear Reel
                </button>
                <button id="btn-generar" class="btn-action btn-primary dock-btn-volante" onclick="generarVolante()">
                    🖼️ Volante
                </button>
                <button class="btn-action dock-btn-ab" onclick="generarVariantesAB()">
                    🔀 Variantes A/B (2 volantes)
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-lote" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content modal-campana-content">
            <div class="modal-campana-header">
                <h2>📦 Lote completado</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-campana-body">
                <p id="lote-resumen" style="font-size:13px; color:#666; margin:0 0 12px;"></p>
                <div id="lote-resultados-grid" class="lote-resultados-grid"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-campana-footer">
                <div class="modal-campana-acciones">
                    <button type="button" class="btn-action btn-dark" onclick="cerrarModalLote()">Cerrar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-ab" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content" style="max-width: 720px; max-height: 92vh; overflow-y: auto;">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Variantes A/B listas 🔀</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666;">Compara dos títulos con los mismos productos.</p>
            <div class="campana-grid">
                <div>
                    <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; margin: 0 0 6px;" id="ab-label-a">Variante A</p>
                    <img id="ab-img-a" src="" alt="Variante A" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; border:1px solid #eee;">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; margin: 0 0 6px;" id="ab-label-b">Variante B</p>
                    <img id="ab-img-b" src="" alt="Variante B" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px; border:1px solid #eee;">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center; margin-top:16px;">
                <button type="button" class="btn-action btn-dark" onclick="guardarVarianteAB('a')">📤 Guardar A</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn-action btn-dark" onclick="guardarVarianteAB('b')">📤 Guardar B</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn-action" style="background:#e0e0e0;color:#333;" onclick="cerrarModalAB()">Cerrar</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-resultado" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: var(--secondary);">¡Diseño Listo! 🎉</h2>
            <img id="imagen-resultado" src="" alt="Volante">
            
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                <a id="btn-descargar" class="btn-action btn-primary" style="text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;" href="#" download="volante.png" onclick="return descargarVolanteActual(event)">⬇️ Descargar Imagen</a>
                <button id="btn-compartir-imagen" class="btn-action btn-dark" style="display: none;" onclick="compartirImagen()">📤 Guardar en iPad</button>
                <button class="btn-action" style="background: #e0e0e0; color: #333;" onclick="cerrarModal()">Cerrar</button>
            </div>
            <div id="hint-imagen-ios" class="ios-hint">
                💡 En iPad: también puedes <strong>mantener pulsada</strong> la imagen y elegir <strong>"Guardar en Fotos"</strong>.
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: left; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px dashed #ccc;">
                <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">📝 Copy para Redes Sociales:</h3>
                <textarea id="texto-copy" readonly style="width: 100%; height: 120px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; resize: none; font-size: 13px;"></textarea>
                <button onclick="copiarCopy()" class="btn-action btn-dark" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px;">📋 Copiar Texto</button>
                <button onclick="compartirWhatsApp()" class="btn-action btn-whatsapp" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 8px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px;">💬 Enviar copy por WhatsApp</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-campana" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content modal-campana-content">
            <div class="modal-campana-header">
                <h2>¡Campaña completa lista! 🚀</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="modal-campana-body">
                <div class="campana-grid">
                    <div>
                        <p style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: center;">📱 Feed</p>
                        <img id="campana-feed-img" src="" alt="Volante feed">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 6px; text-align: center;">📲 Historia</p>
                        <img id="campana-historia-img" src="" alt="Volante historia">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <video id="campana-reel-video" controls playsinline></video>
                <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px dashed #ccc;">
                    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #555;">📝 Copy para redes:</h3>
                    <textarea id="campana-copy" readonly></textarea>
                </div>
                <p id="hint-campana-ios" class="ios-hint" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    💡 En iPad usa <strong>Guardar</strong> en cada archivo — se abre el menú compartir sin salir del panel.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="modal-campana-footer">
                <p class="footer-label" id="campana-footer-label-archivos">Descargar archivos</p>
                <div class="modal-campana-acciones">
                    <button type="button" id="btn-dl-feed" class="btn-action btn-dark" onclick="guardarCampanaArchivo('feed')">⬇️ Feed</button>
                    <button type="button" id="btn-dl-historia" class="btn-action btn-dark" onclick="guardarCampanaArchivo('historia')">⬇️ Historia</button>
                    <button type="button" id="btn-dl-reel" class="btn-action btn-dark" onclick="guardarCampanaArchivo('reel')">⬇️ Reel</button>
